- Bate com força.

930
01:12:44,418 --> 01:12:45,419
Qual é!

931
01:12:48,380 --> 01:12:49,589
Tem medo de me machucar?

932
01:12:54,177 --> 01:12:55,178
Covarde.

933
01:12:58,724 --> 01:12:59,725
Espera!

934
01:13:05,564 --> 01:13:06,565
Ok?

935
01:13:13,864 --> 01:13:15,323
Tenta realmente vencer.

936
01:13:17,993 --> 01:13:18,994
Por favor.

937
01:13:41,058 --> 01:13:42,350
- Ei.
- Estou bem.

